                        </div>

                        <div class="ex_item">
                            n - ammount of x numbers
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <div class="function_container">
                <div class="heading_container">
                    <h3>Simple mean Calculator</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="description_function">
                    <p>Try simple mean calculator. Input few numbers and calculate mean of the numbers. </p>
                </div>

                <div class="input_box">
                    <label>Number:</label>
                    <input @bind="number_1" />
                </div>


                <button class="btn" @onclick="Add_Number_1">Add Number</button>
                <button class="btn" @onclick="Reset_1">Reset</button>
